snippet.title: Strike Force Heroes - Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
An oldschool arena shooter rebuilt with modern mechanics, with full co-operative & PvP online multiplayer. It melds over the top action with epic story-telling in this intense remake of the hit Flash game.

Available now on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1981820/Strike_Force_Heroes/
